author: Isabelle Philippe
title: We've faced coronavirus outbreaks before. Here's why COVID-19 has many people scared.
description: The alarm COVID-19 has generated within the United States is unprecedented.
content:
In the last 20 years, the United States has faced a number of potentially deadly coronavirus outbreaks.
